description.p:
Analogous advantages and effects may be associated with a method in accordance with the present disclosure, which is a method of servicing any one of the above-described waste bins. In this method, the waste bin further is further configured to output a value W measured by the weight sensor and a value L measured by the level sensor. The method comprises the steps of
(a) comparing the value W to a predetermined weight value PW;
(b) comparing the value L to a predetermined fill level value PL;
(c) if L≥PL and W<PW, compressing the waste in the compartment;
(d) if L≥PL and W≥PW, emptying the compartment.
